Package: centerline
Title: Extract Centerline from a Closed Polygons
Version: 0.0.5
Authors@R:
    c(
      person(given = "Anatoly",
             family = "Tsyplenkov",
             role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
             email = "atsyplenkov@fastmail.com",
             comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4144-8402"))
    )
Maintainer: Anatoly Tsyplenkov <atsyplenkov@fastmail.com>
Description: The {centerline} package simplifies the extraction of linear 
    features from closed 2D polygons, by computing their 
    centerlines (or median-axis) using Voronoi diagrams.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/atsyplenkov/centerline
